260
00:30:03,139 --> 00:30:04,179
<font color=#FFFF00>Ahhh...</font>

261
00:30:05,109 --> 00:30:06,238
<font color=#FFFF00>Gugatan?</font>

262
00:30:06,478 --> 00:30:09,508
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa menurutmu ini akan membuatku
membatalkan tuntutan hukumnya?</font>

263
00:30:10,349 --> 00:30:11,449
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan itu.</font>

264
00:30:11,449 --> 00:30:13,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu kalau gitu kenapa kau kemari?</font>

265
00:30:13,919 --> 00:30:16,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bukan robot, jadi kenapa masih kemari?</font>

266
00:30:18,389 --> 00:30:22,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak mengerti apa yang sudah kau
lakukan? terhadapku selama ini, bukan?</font>

267
00:30:23,659 --> 00:30:24,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah kutunjukkan?</font>

268
00:30:39,579 --> 00:30:40,679
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

269
00:30:41,978 --> 00:30:44,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir menular? Atau mungkin...</font>

270
00:30:45,419 --> 00:30:46,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau takut?</font>

271
00:30:46,649 --> 00:30:48,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan begitu... Tidak akan,</font>

272
00:30:48,248 --> 00:30:50,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak takut saat menjadi robot.</font>

273
00:30:50,349 --> 00:30:51,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat jadi manusia kau takut?</font>

274
00:30:52,718 --> 00:30:53,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu bukan itu.</font>

275
00:30:53,988 --> 00:30:55,558
<font color=#FFFF00>Apanya yang bukan?</font>

276
00:31:03,028 --> 00:31:04,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah jawabanku.</font>

277
00:31:06,298 --> 00:31:07,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Enyah!</font>

278
00:31:25,258 --> 00:31:26,659
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku minta maaf.</i></font>

279
00:31:27,988 --> 00:31:29,089
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tapi,</i></font>

280
00:31:30,058 --> 00:31:32,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak takut sama sekali.</font>

281
00:31:35,129 --> 00:31:39,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak peduli apa yang kau katakan padaku...</font>

282
00:31:40,139 --> 00:31:42,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Apapun perlakuanmu, aku akan kembali.</font>

283
00:31:44,839 --> 00:31:46,978
<font color=#FFFF00>Besok... lusa...</font>

